          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χρεώ</span></b> , <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χρεώ,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Il. 11.606</span></i>, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            χρειώ</span> (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χρή</span>): <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">want,
            need, necessity;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χρειοῖ ἀναγκαίῃ,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Il. 8.57</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc"> ἐστὶ,
            γίγνεται</span> (cf. opus est), w. gen. of thing and acc. of
          person, also freq. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ικει, ἱκά̄νει,
            ἱκά̄νεται,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Od. 6.136</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            χρέω</span> without <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐστί</span> or
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἱκά̄νει</span>, like <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χρή, τίπτε δέ σε χρεώ; </span>
